events.title: Graduating highschool
events.content: This is my last year in highschool. It's weird. I'll kinda miss this.

events.title: First time to take a computer science course
events.content: I chose to take computer science as one of my electives. I had always been midly interested in it because it is what my dad does for work. I did enjoy it!

events.title: Started Highschool
events.content: First school in new country! I was so scared of talking in a new language but I was able to!

events.title: Moved to canada
events.content: I finally moved from Peru to Canada! It was a big adjustment but it was the best decisions my parents made. I can't imagine myself still living in Peru.
